            <title><![CDATA[Granblue Fantasy Versus: Rising DLC character Id, Switch 2 version announced]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/06/granblue-fantasy-versus-rising-dlc-character-id-switch-2-version-announced</link>
            <guid>1563016</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PS4</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Due out on September 17.</span>
      </p></div><div><p>Publisher <a title="Companies > Cygames [285 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/cyberagent/cygames">Cygames</a> and developer <a title="Companies > Arc System Works [1,340 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/arc-system-works">Arc System Works</a> have <a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000001272.000005593.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">announced</a> <em><a title="Games > Granblue Fantasy Versus: Rising [39 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/granblue-fantasy-versus-rising">Granblue Fantasy Versus: Rising</a></em> downloadable content character Id from <em><a title="Games > Granblue Fantasy: Relink [53 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/granblue-fantasy-relink">Granblue Fantasy: Relink</a></em>, as well as a <a title="Platforms > Switch 2 [1,049 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a> version of game. Both the new character and Switch 2 version will launch alongside the version 2.60 update on September 17. <span id="more-1045577"></span></p><p>The version 2.60 update will include the following contents:</p><ul><li>New downloadable content character Id</li><li>New stage</li><li>New system mechanic</li><li>Adjustments to system mechanics</li><li>Character adjustments</li><li>New costume</li><li>…and more!</li></ul><figure><a data-featherlight="image" href="https://www.gematsu.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/GBVS-Update_06-27-26.jpg"></a></figure><figure><a data-featherlight="image" href="https://www.gematsu.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/GBVS-Switch-2_06-27-26.jpg"></a></figure><p><em>Granblue Fantasy Versus: Rising</em> is available now for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [11,514 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [28,737 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [25,613 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2157560/Granblue_Fantasy_Versus_Rising/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>.</p><!-- AD: content -->
        <p>Watch a new trailer below.</p><h2><span>DLC Character Id Teaser / Switch 2 Announce Trailer</span></h2><p><strong>English</strong></p><p><iframe title="Granblue Fantasy Versus: Rising – Id Teaser" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/2xLBpWBZ1ek?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Japanese</strong></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="『Granblue Fantasy Versus: Rising』 #48 「イド参戦編（ティザーバージョン）」" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/1KI8Ao16tx0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/06/granblue-fantasy-versus-rising-dlc-character-id-switch-2-version-announced]]></content:encoded>
